Register the VFIO_IRQ_TYPE_NESTED/VFIO_IRQ_SUBTYPE_DMA_FAULT
IRQ that allows to signal a nested mode DMA fault.

Signed-off-by: Eric Auger <eric.auger@redhat.com>
